description:
This is a 25 minute workout called 'HIIT Workout - High Intensity Intervals | GCN 25 Minute Bike Session' from the channel Global Cycling Network.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging and Moderate.

Original workout description: Train to win! Are you ready for high intensity workout? Try this 25 minute indoor cycling training session featuring high intensity intervals. 

Subscribe to GCN Training: https://gcn.eu/GCNTraining

Subscribe to GCN: http://gcn.eu/SubscribeToGCN
Get exclusive GCN gear in the GCN shop! http://gcn.eu/9a

Join the GCN team and special guests for a challenging, high energy and high intensity session. This 25 minute blast will prepare you for your next intense physical challenge, prepare yourself physically and mentally for the journey ahead! This is ideal for an indoor bike or for your turbo trainer. Try it and let us know how you get on down in the comments ðŸ‘‡
